  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Provides for the repeal of the Mauna Kea Stewardship and Oversight Authority and reversion of management authority over Mauna Kea lands to the University of Hawaii if the timelines specified in Act 255, SLH 2022, are not met.  Establishes a deadline of 7/1/2030 for the transfer of appropriations, records, equipment, and other property to the Mauna Kea Stewardship and Oversight Authority.  Authorizes the Authority to extend existing leases and subleases for up to an additional 10-year term.  Effective 7/1/2050.  (SD2)"
    }
  ],
